  - family-names: Maicovschi
    given-names: Maxim Tudor
repository-code: "https://github.com/Systemartis/clyde"
url: "https://github.com/Systemartis/clyde"
license: MIT
keywords:
  - tui
  - terminal
  - claude
  - claude-code
  - bubbletea
  - go
abstract: >-
  A single-binary Go TUI that tiles next to your `claude` pane and surfaces
  per-project Claude Code session state — live sessions, tool calls, token
  usage, todos, subagents, MCP servers — without leaving the terminal.
